---
title: Cal Smart Chipotle-Honey Tofu Bowls with Green Onion Rice
description: This hearty tofu bowl is full of wholesome goodness! We even snuck some spinach into the tofu mix for an added veggie boost. Pickled radishes and a sweet and spicy chipotle-honey sauce brighten each bite.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/bols-de-tofu-a-la-sauce-au-chipotle-et-au-miel-c1857028.jpg
